Package: InteractiveWordcloud
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Wordcloud
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Elizabeth Law
Maintainer: Elizabeth Law <workingconservation@gmail.com>
Description: An R script that delivers an open, interactive word cloud (links R with Google Forms)
    Participants can input to the Google form, when they submit their answer it gets entered into 
    the linked Google sheet. Then, this script automates download of the Google sheet, cleans and 
    prepares the data, and plots to a wordcloud. This can be run iteratively to provide an 
    interactive audience participation experience.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1),
    magrittr
Imports: 
    googledrive,
    readr,
    dplyr,
    tm,
    wordcloud2
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
